#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:224 includes/admin/review-setting.php:261
msgid "4 weeks (1 month)"
msgstr "4 semanas (1 mes)"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:225 includes/admin/review-setting.php:263
msgid "Custom..."
msgstr "Personalizado..."

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:230 includes/admin/review-setting.php:268
msgid "Value"
msgstr "Valor"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:232 includes/admin/review-setting.php:270
msgid "Hours"
msgstr "Horario"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:233 includes/admin/review-setting.php:271
msgid "Days"
msgstr "Días"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:238
msgid ""
"Time to wait after order status change before sending review request to "
"customers."
msgstr ""
"Tiempo de espera tras el cambio de estado del pedido antes de enviar la "
"solicitud de valoración a los clientes."

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:247
msgid "Handle international orders differently"
msgstr "Gestionar los pedidos internacionales de forma diferente"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:249
msgid ""
"When enabled, international orders will use a separate, longer review "
"request delay. This gives international customers more time to receive and "
"verify their orders."
msgstr ""
"Cuando esta opción esté activada, los pedidos internacionales tendrán un "
"plazo de solicitud de revisión independiente y más largo. Esto permite a los"
" clientes internacionales disponer de más tiempo para recibir y verificar "
"sus pedidos."

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:253
msgid "International Order Review Request Delay"
msgstr "Retraso en la solicitud de revisión de un pedido internacional"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:255
msgid "International Delay"
msgstr "Retraso internacional"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:262
msgid "8 weeks (2 months)"
msgstr "8 semanas (2 meses)"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:276
msgid ""
"International shipments typically take longer. Set a longer delay to ensure "
"customers receive and verify orders before review requests arrive."
msgstr ""
"Los envíos internacionales suelen tardar más tiempo. Establece un plazo más "
"largo para garantizar que los clientes reciban y comprueben los pedidos "
"antes de que lleguen las solicitudes de valoración."

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:282
msgid "Service-Specific Settings"
msgstr "Configuración específica del servicio"

